  <p>Set a hint for the window manager, requesting that the titlebar
should be hidden when the window is maximized.</p>  <p>Note that this property is automatically updated by GTK+, so this
function should only be used by applications which do not use GTK+
to create toplevel windows.</p>
  <p>Since 3.4</p>
